0be%20too%20intrusive%20within%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%20I%20agree%2C%20the%20walkway%20cuts%20through%20the%20forest%20with%20finesse%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20way%20of%20hope%20through%20the%20urban%20sprawl%20that%20skirts%20around%20its%20perimeter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20trees%20were%20cut%20for%20the%20project.%E2%80%9D%20The%20walkway%20has%20found%20its%20safe%20space%2C%20its%20Merbau%20wood%20torso%20supported%20by%20epoxy-coated%20steel%20columns%2C%20cradled%20by%20the%20land%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20huge%20hammock%20that%20finds%20support%20in%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20beams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20walk%20is%20punctuated%20by%20nameplates%20that%20bear%20mention%20of%20the%20different%20species%20of%20birds%20that%20call%20this%20forest%20home%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebulbuls%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20parakeets.%20The%20walk%20boasts%20pockets%20of%20unprecedented%20stillness%2C%20broken%20only%20by%20the%20sounds%20of%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Came%20here%20as%20a%20boy%20of%2011%20years%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20the%20architect%20who%20built%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20Rahul%20Kadri%3F%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20I%20have%20a%20picture%20with%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoes%20of%20admiration%20follow%20Rahul%20all%20along