%20nature%20trail%20is%20made%20of%20wood%20and%20supported%20by%20steel%3B%20sustainability%20is%20in%20the%20details%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20walk%20the%20walkway%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20what%20Iftikhar%20meant.%20The%20structure%20is%20an%20aesthetic%20argument%20for%20how%20beauty%20does%20not%20have%20to%20come%20at%20a%20cost%20to%20nature.%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20proclivity%20towards%20designing%2C%20keeping%20nature%20in%20mind%2C%20stems%20from%20his%20childhood%2C%20which%20was%20marked%20by%20a%20rendezvous%20with%20the%20natural%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20boarding%20school%20in%20Nainital%20at%20the%20age%20of%20eight.%20Sherwood%20College%20is%20up%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20There%20were%20forests%20all%20around%20us.%20From%20our%20playfields%2C%20we%20could%20actually%20walk%20into%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20forest%2C%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20Rahul%20playing.%20Instead%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20see%20him%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F415182%2Ftrekking-with-kids-beginner-friendly-trails-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20the%20wilderness%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Around%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20the%20Malabar%20area%20in%20Mumbai%20shared%20ground%20with%20hyenas%20and%20jackals.%C2%A0With%20time%2C%20buildings%20and%20skyscrapers%20dotted%20its%20skyline%2C%20and%20what%20remained%20of%20the%20jungle%20was%20a%2012-acre%20microbiome%20where%20rose-ringed%20parakeet%2C%20coppersmith%20barbet%2C%20and%20golden%20oriole%20continue%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20walks%20along%20the%20nature%20trail%2C%20a%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu%20creeps%20up%20on%20him.%20He%20recalls%20venturing%20into%20the%20Malabar%20Forest%20when%20he%20was%20around%2011%20years%20old%20with%20his%20dog%2C%20walking%2C%20exploring%2C%20and%20wondering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20afraid%20of%20being%20in%20the%20forest%20by%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20known%20to%20find%20pathways%2C%20to%20intuitively%20know%20the%20way.%E2%80%9D%20He%20did%20not%20need%20a%20GPS%2C%20he%20was%20guided%20by%20the%20rhythms%20of%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20design%20philosophy%20backed%20by%20sustainable%20sensibilities%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesign%20viability%20and%20beautiful%20views%20convene%20in%20the%20nature%20trail%3B%20its%20Sea%20Viewing%20Deck%20offering%20the%20average%20visitor%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20their%20city%20through%20a%20new%20lens.%20Through%20the%20482%20metres%20it%20covers%2C%20the%20walkway%20embodies%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20vision%20for%20nature%20to%20become%20a%20centrepiece%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F419684%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-using-stone-lime-moss-the-timber-residence-vagator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20architecture%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elevated%20walkway%20begins%20on%20Siri%20Road%20behind%20the%20Kamala%20Nehru%20Park%20and%20ends%20in%20the%20verdant%20sprawl%20of%20the%20Doongerwadi%20Woods.%20Segueing%20into%20the%20conversation%20of%20how%20the%20project%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Rahul%20backtracks%20to%20one%20of%20his%20walks%20through%20this%20stretch%20during%20the%20COVID-19-induced%20lockdown%2C%20when%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20exploring%20the%20neighbourhood.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20climbed%20over%20the%20fence.%20That%20was%20the%20day%20it%20all%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20What%20followed%20were%20weeks%20of%20%E2%80%9Creading%20the%20site%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20in%20understanding%20how%20the%20site%20works.%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20more%20than%20many%20architects%2C%C2%A0%20imagining%20my%20building.%20I%20love%20to%20be%20on%20the%20site%20alone%20and%20need%20quiet.%20I%20get%20a%20deep%2C%20intuitive%20sense%20of%20how%20things%20need%20to%20unfold.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Malabar%20Forest%20is%20home%20to%20numerous%20species%20of%20birds%20such%20as%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%20and%20parakeets%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-420973%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Malabar%20Forest%20is%20home%20to%20numerous%20species%20of%20birds%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%20and%20parakeets%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20walks%20along%20the%20perimeters%2C%20the%20pockets%20and%20every%20corner.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20to%20see%20every%20part%20of%20it%20to%20see%20where%20I%20can%20build%20with%20the%20lightest%20touch%20and%20the%20maximum%20effect.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20walkway%2C%20the%20idea%20for%20a%20raised%20platform%20was%20hinged%20on%20wanting%20to%20cause%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309795%2Fbengaluru-architect-builds-sustainable-stone-clay-holiday-home-around-nature%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleast%20disruption%20to%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20said%2C%20if%20people%20are%20going%20to%20come%20in%20here%2C%20how%20do%20we%20make%20sure%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20into%20the%20forest%20in%20a%20way%20that%20disturbs%20it%3F%20Considering%20this%20is%20a%20hill%20slope%2C%20another%20concern%20was%20how%20not%20to%20disturb%20the%20flow%20of%20water.%20The%20third%20was%20the%20reptiles.%20Once%20people%20began%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20path%2C%20they%20would%20interact%20with%20the%20snakes%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20prevent%20that.%20The%20best%20approach%20was%20to%20lift%20the%20path%20off%20the%20forest%20floor.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20and%20the%20team%20wanted%20to%20draw%20upon%20conventional%20wisdom%20and%20use%20sal%20wood%20that%20has%20been%20employed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20for%20years%2C%20they%20found%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386381%2Fpunjab-parminder-singh-turning-agri-waste-into-eco-friendly-tiles-prevent-stubble-burning-air-pollution-delhi-ncr-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20more%20sustainable%20bet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20zeroed%20in%20on%20teak%20grown%20in%20Kerala%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20durable%20and%20does%20not%20need%20polishing%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20support%20the%20walkway%20from%20below%20with%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20lightweight%2C%20sleeker%2C%20and%20easier%20to%20maintain%20over%20time.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20concrete%20because%20it%20would%20mess%20the%20forest%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20brainwave%2C%20every%20idea%2C%20and%20every%20decision%20has%20led%20to%20this%20beautiful%20composite%20that%20is%20the%20walkway.%20To%20say%20that%20Rahul%20has%20built%20Mumbai%20a%20walkway%20will%20be%20to%20trivialise%20what%20he%20has%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20I%20see%20it%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20given%20every%20person%20in%20this%20city%20a%20customised%20gift.%20To%20the%20siblings%20and%20their%20dad%2C%20the%20walkway%20is%20an%20excuse%20for%20an%20outing.%20To%20the%20gaggle%20of%20women%2C%20it%20is%20a%20reason%20for%20a%20morning%20walk%20and%20to%20the%20elderly%20uncle%20duo%20%E2%80%94%20I%20never%20found%20out%20the%20joke%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20reason%20for%20them%20to%20smile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20me%2C%20it%20is%20a%20reason%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20Mumbai%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20IMK%20Architects%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744815600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway_11zon-1744813466.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D420963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Malabar%20nature%20trail%20is%20cradled%20by%20the%20microbiome%20of%20the%20Malabar%20Forest.%20Principal%20architect%20Rahul%20Kadri%20takes%20us%20on%20a%20guided%20tour%20of%20the%20walkway%2C%20where%20he%20explains%20the%20design%20philosophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F420963%2Fmalabar-forest-nature-trail-built-by-rahul-kadri-imk-architects-sustainable-architecture-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3